name: Sonny Crockett from Miami Vice - Don Johnson
description:
The character James "Sonny" Crockett from Miami Vice as portrayed by Don Johnson
Made using stills from the series and promotional images.

Sorry for the delay, ran into some hiccups getting his look 'right'.

Training Details:
14 images, +12.5k steps, using SD 1.5 base model.
